Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.45,0:00:56.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,闇にそびえ立つ摩天楼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.45,0:00:56.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,スターサイドホテル
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.65,0:00:54.17,default,,0,0,0,,The tall building that\Nlooms in the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.17,0:00:55.30,default,,0,0,0,,The Starside Hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.62,0:01:01.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その一角で行われる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.62,0:01:01.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今宵のファイナルステージ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.70,0:01:00.40,default,,0,0,0,,The final stage is taking place\Nin a small corner of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.26,0:01:06.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それは地上74メートルに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.26,0:01:06.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,架けられた鉄骨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.29,0:01:05.94,default,,0,0,0,,It's a gamble of death by\Ncrossing a steel beam,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.46,0:01:10.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,全長25メートルを渡る
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.46,0:01:10.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死の橋渡り
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.50,0:01:10.45,default,,0,0,0,,25 metres in length,\N74 metres from the ground...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.67,0:01:13.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クソッ クソッ　やるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.68,0:01:13.37,default,,0,0,0,,Darn it, darn it!\NI'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.34,0:01:16.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やりゃあいいんだろ　クソが！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.37,0:01:16.29,default,,0,0,0,,All I have to do is\Ncross, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.84,0:01:20.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジたちは今 摩天の地獄
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.85,0:01:20.12,default,,0,0,0,,Under the cold sky,\NKaiji and the rest...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.31,0:01:22.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その入り口に立っている
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.35,0:01:22.63,default,,0,0,0,,...are about to challenge\Ntheir worst fears.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.47,0:01:24.93,kaiji-main-top,,0,0,0,,Monster
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.75,0:01:35.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これで８人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.75,0:01:35.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうする？ほかの者は決したぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.78,0:01:33.32,default,,0,0,0,,That makes eight of you.\NWhat about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.32,0:01:34.80,default,,0,0,0,,The rest have decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.69,0:01:39.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,参加か？それとも権利放棄か
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.84,0:01:39.08,default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to take part\Nor forgo your chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.43,0:01:46.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,な 何を…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.43,0:01:46.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やらぬ者が持っていても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.62,0:01:44.75,default,,0,0,0,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.75,0:01:47.40,default,,0,0,0,,They can't hold the tickets.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.14,0:01:49.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,仕方あるまい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.14,0:01:49.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これは３着以下に譲ろう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.64,0:01:49.78,default,,0,0,0,,These are for\Nthe third place and lower!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.71,0:01:51.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お願いです　もう少し待って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.71,0:01:51.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょっと そんな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.00,0:01:51.78,default,,0,0,0,,- Hey, you can't!\N- Please wait a while more!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.64,0:01:56.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クズが！話にならぬ クズ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.78,0:01:52.79,default,,0,0,0,,You trash!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.79,0:01:55.66,default,,0,0,0,,No point talking\Nto you, trash!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.21,0:01:58.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう少し待ってくれ？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.27,0:01:57.93,default,,0,0,0,,Please wait a little\Nwhile more?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.28,0:02:02.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前らは生まれてから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.28,0:02:02.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何度 そのセリフを吐いた？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.42,0:02:01.40,default,,0,0,0,,You've said that countless times\Nsince you were born, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.31,0:02:04.84,default,,0,0,0,,The society isn't here\Nto mother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.32,0:02:04.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,世間はお前らの母親ではない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.99,0:02:08.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クズの決心を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.99,0:02:08.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いつまでも待ったりはせん
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.08,0:02:07.40,default,,0,0,0,,Nobody will wait for trash like\Nyou to make up their minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.39,0:02:12.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一生 迷ってろ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.39,0:02:12.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして失い続けるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.41,0:02:10.02,default,,0,0,0,,You can stay lost forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.41,0:02:14.38,default,,0,0,0,,All your valuable chances\Nwill go to waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.66,0:02:14.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,貴重なチャンスを
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.43,0:02:22.56,default,,0,0,0,,The first and second place ticket,\Nfirst-come-first-served.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.44,0:02:22.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１着券と２着券 先着順だ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.47,0:02:25.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,我こそは と思う者は申し出ろ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.56,0:02:24.72,default,,0,0,0,,Those who want it...\Ncome forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.58,0:02:28.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺が！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.58,0:02:28.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,や やります
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.60,0:02:26.61,default,,0,0,0,,It'll be me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.35,0:02:28.89,default,,0,0,0,,I-I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.26,0:02:34.89,default,,0,0,0,,The 10 tickets for this last\Nstage have been given out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.28,0:02:35.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,決勝 10枚のチケットは
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.28,0:02:35.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すべてさばかれた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.62,0:02:39.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,同時にこのファイナルレースに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.62,0:02:39.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,不参加の者は
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.67,0:02:39.15,default,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, those who aren't\Nparticipating in the final stage...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.15,0:02:41.37,default,,0,0,0,,...are herded away\Nby the men in black.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.16,0:02:41.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,黒服によってステージを去り
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.66,0:02:46.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,残された10名は 橋を渡る順番を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.66,0:02:46.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,決めるよう指示される
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.69,0:02:46.64,default,,0,0,0,,The 10 remaining will wait for\Ninstructions to cross the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.83,0:02:52.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,信じよう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.86,0:02:50.01,default,,0,0,0,,Let's believe in it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.59,0:02:56.22,default,,0,0,0,,Though I'm not Tonegawa,\Nwe've managed to cross it once.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.60,0:02:56.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,利根川じゃねえが
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.60,0:02:56.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,みんな 一度は渡った橋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.97,0:03:00.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,渡れる　渡れるはずだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.09,0:02:59.25,default,,0,0,0,,It can be crossed!\NIt should be possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.23,0:03:01.25,default,,0,0,0,,Let's believe!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.24,0:03:03.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,信じよう　自分たちを
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.91,0:03:03.22,default,,0,0,0,,Believe in yourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.82,0:03:15.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,渡れる　俺たちは渡れる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.85,0:03:10.98,default,,0,0,0,,It can be done...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.82,0:03:14.00,default,,0,0,0,,We can cross this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.20,0:03:17.44,default,,0,0,0,,Let's believe that\Nwe can cross it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.22,0:03:19.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,｢信じよう｣｢渡れる｣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.22,0:03:19.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その言葉がすべて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.63,0:03:23.13,default,,0,0,0,,They kept chanting those words\Nin a bid to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.56,0:03:23.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,生き残るため
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.56,0:03:23.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,彼らはその言葉を口にする
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.80,0:03:28.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何というか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.80,0:03:28.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,少しもったいない気もしますね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.84,0:03:27.48,default,,0,0,0,,How should I put it...\NI feel that it's such a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.64,0:03:31.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ギャンブルとして
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.64,0:03:31.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これ以上ない ショーだというのに
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.68,0:03:31.86,default,,0,0,0,,There's no show with\Na greater gamble than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.67,0:03:34.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,橋の向こうの部屋の方々は
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.86,0:03:34.22,default,,0,0,0,,Yet there're people who are\Nwatching them cross...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.11,0:03:37.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,テレビカメラでとらえた映像と
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.11,0:03:37.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,渡ってくる やつらを
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.22,0:03:37.70,default,,0,0,0,,...through the eyes of\Na TV camera,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.68,0:03:42.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただ食事をしながら
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.68,0:03:42.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見物しておられるだけだなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.70,0:03:41.18,default,,0,0,0,,just observing as they\Nhave their meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.30,0:03:45.26,default,,0,0,0,,It's all right. They're still\Nenjoying themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.32,0:03:47.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいのさ　めでるだけで
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.32,0:03:47.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あちらの方々は
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.70,0:03:50.92,default,,0,0,0,,They weren't the ones\Nscreaming away under the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.19,0:03:51.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,下の橋でバカ騒ぎしていた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.19,0:03:51.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,成り金どもとは違う
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.39,0:03:54.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,金の世界を牛耳る本物のＶＩＰ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.39,0:03:56.01,default,,0,0,0,,They're the true wealthy people\Nwho dominate the world of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.40,0:03:57.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,資産家だ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.03,0:04:00.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ギャンブルなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.03,0:04:00.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう とっくに卒業してらっしゃる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.08,0:04:00.72,default,,0,0,0,,They have long graduated from\Nthe arena called gambling.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.90,0:04:04.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あんなものは
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.90,0:04:04.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,貧乏人のやることとな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.94,0:04:04.25,default,,0,0,0,,Such things are for\Nthe poor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.08,0:04:11.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,賭けずともいい
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.08,0:04:11.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,賭けずとも十分 楽しめるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.09,0:04:10.93,default,,0,0,0,,They can still enjoy themselves,\Neven if they don't gamble.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.88,0:04:17.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人が恐れおののき 泣きながら
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.88,0:04:17.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,不安定な橋を渡っていく
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.96,0:04:16.58,default,,0,0,0,,The sight of people being terrified\Nat crossing an unstable bridge...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.12,0:04:20.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのさまを
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.12,0:04:20.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,安定した場所から見ている
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.17,0:04:19.99,default,,0,0,0,,Being able to see that from\Na place of comfort,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.99,0:04:22.27,default,,0,0,0,,is more than enough\Nfor them to enjoy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.02,0:04:23.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう それだけで感じられるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.33,0:04:27.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,安全という名の愉悦をな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.34,0:04:25.77,default,,0,0,0,,Watching it without\Nrisking their lives...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.03,0:04:29.62,default,,0,0,0,,That kind of pleasure is\Nmore than you'd expect.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.06,0:04:30.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これが思いのほか 美味でな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.97,0:04:34.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから賭ける必要などないのさ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.09,0:04:33.78,default,,0,0,0,,There's no reason\Nto gamble.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.80,0:04:39.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さて 役得だ　高見の見物といくか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.86,0:04:36.56,default,,0,0,0,,Well then, time to\Nenjoy ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.83,0:04:42.02,default,,0,0,0,,We get the best view as spectators,\Nwatching trash becoming stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.18,0:04:42.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クズどもが星になるさまを
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.95,0:04:47.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝てば救いの大金
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.95,0:04:47.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし負ければ落下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.01,0:04:45.00,default,,0,0,0,,If they win, they'll survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.00,0:04:49.05,default,,0,0,0,,But if they lose, they'll\Nundoubtedly fall to their deaths!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.25,0:04:51.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まごうことなき死
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.25,0:04:51.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,掛け値なしの絶体絶命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.05,0:04:51.23,default,,0,0,0,,It's a deadly situation\Nwith no turning back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.97,0:04:55.50,default,,0,0,0,,And the order to cross\Nthe death bridge is out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.99,0:04:56.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして決す
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.99,0:04:56.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死の架け橋を渡る順番
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.16,0:04:59.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,右の橋の先頭は太田 以下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.24,0:04:59.08,default,,0,0,0,,The order for the right bridge\Nwill be Oota,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.00,0:05:02.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,佐原 西田 藤野 秋川と続く
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.08,0:05:02.00,default,,0,0,0,,followed by Sahara, Nisida,\NFujino, and Akikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.43,0:05:04.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,左の橋の先頭は中村
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.56,0:05:06.12,default,,0,0,0,,Nakamura will be the first\Nto cross the left bridge,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.97,0:05:09.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これに中山 カイジ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.97,0:05:09.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,石田 小泉が続く
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.12,0:05:09.01,default,,0,0,0,,followed by Nakayama, Kaiji,\NIshida and Koizumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.61,0:05:14.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺が… 俺が１番… １番
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.64,0:05:12.25,default,,0,0,0,,I'm the first one...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.17,0:05:14.14,default,,0,0,0,,First one...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.51,0:05:19.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,渡れる　太田 俺たちは渡れる
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.63,0:05:15.98,default,,0,0,0,,You can cross it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.36,0:05:18.59,default,,0,0,0,,Oota! We can cross it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.08,0:05:22.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,渡れるんだ　足を貸せ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.19,0:05:20.38,default,,0,0,0,,We can cross it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.02,0:05:22.96,default,,0,0,0,,Show me your feet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.99,0:05:25.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいから早く
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.14,0:05:25.50,default,,0,0,0,,Just do it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.62,0:05:26.46,default,,0,0,0,,Feet?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.62,0:05:27.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,足？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.76,0:05:34.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これは半ば おまじない
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.76,0:05:34.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが 半ば照準だ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.82,0:05:32.69,default,,0,0,0,,Half of this is for luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.15,0:05:34.82,default,,0,0,0,,The other is to adjust the aim.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.63,0:05:37.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,照準？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.82,0:05:35.87,default,,0,0,0,,Aim?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.30,0:05:42.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この線と鉄骨に刻まれた中心線を
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.30,0:05:42.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,合わせて歩くんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.36,0:05:41.31,default,,0,0,0,,Always align this line right in\Nthe centre of the steel beam.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.57,0:05:44.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それだけに集中して歩く
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.68,0:05:47.11,default,,0,0,0,,As long as you focus on that, you'll\Ndefinitely get to the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.97,0:05:47.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,気がつけば向こう側に着いてるさ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.88,0:05:52.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただ この線はあくまで
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.88,0:05:52.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここが足の中心って目安で
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.92,0:05:52.20,default,,0,0,0,,But remember that this line is\Nfor you to aim at your feet,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.18,0:05:55.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本当のそれとは微妙に ずれてる
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.20,0:05:54.40,default,,0,0,0,,and the centre of gravity from\Nyour body will be slightly off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.02,0:05:57.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その辺は歩きながら
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.02,0:05:57.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,微調整してくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.12,0:05:57.40,default,,0,0,0,,So remember to adjust yourself \Naccordingly while crossing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.52,0:05:59.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わ 分かった
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.93,0:05:59.13,default,,0,0,0,,G-Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.46,0:06:02.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君　俺も… 俺にも頼む
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.51,0:06:02.22,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji! Me too!\NPlease do it for me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.16,0:06:04.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺も
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.16,0:06:04.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺も
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.22,0:06:03.13,default,,0,0,0,,M-Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.41,0:06:04.33,default,,0,0,0,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.16,0:06:06.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺にも頼む
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.16,0:06:09.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺も
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.33,0:06:05.13,default,,0,0,0,,Me too please!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.47,0:06:06.28,default,,0,0,0,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.16,0:06:09.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジさん　俺も…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.28,0:06:09.37,default,,0,0,0,,- Me too! Me too!\N- Kaiji, me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.83,0:06:15.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,理が人の心を救うこともある
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.84,0:06:15.19,default,,0,0,0,,Reasons can save people\Nat times,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.14,0:06:18.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,たとえそれが
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.14,0:06:18.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どんなに か細い理であっても
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.19,0:06:18.38,default,,0,0,0,,regardless of how flimsy\Na reasoning is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.91,0:06:23.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今 目の前の状況に
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.91,0:06:23.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,押しつぶされそうな者には救い
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.95,0:06:23.62,default,,0,0,0,,For now, it's saving these people who\Nfear what they are about to face.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.61,0:06:26.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勇気を奮い立たせる
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.61,0:06:26.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,きっかけとなる
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.62,0:06:25.88,default,,0,0,0,,This might be the source of\Ncourage that they need.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.35,0:06:29.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,恐れるな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.35,0:06:29.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,体の中心さえ ずらさなければ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.39,0:06:27.39,default,,0,0,0,,Don't fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.91,0:06:31.62,default,,0,0,0,,Your centre of gravity should be\Nstable so you won't fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.79,0:06:34.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,100パーセント 落ちない
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.79,0:06:34.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,物理的に落ちないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.20,0:06:33.86,default,,0,0,0,,There's no way you will fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.02,0:06:35.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.20,0:06:35.23,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.72,0:06:38.46,default,,0,0,0,,Move forth slowly!\NThere's no need to panic!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.96,0:06:40.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ゆっくり進めばいい
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.96,0:06:40.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,焦らなくていいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.15,0:06:43.64,default,,0,0,0,,This time, it isn't a competition! \NNobody will push you from behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.16,0:06:45.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今度は競争じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.16,0:06:45.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,後ろから押されることはないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.00,0:06:47.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,敵はいない
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.00,0:06:47.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自分のペースで行ける
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.06,0:06:47.88,default,,0,0,0,,There are no enemies! \NJust do it at your own pace!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.88,0:06:50.43,default,,0,0,0,,It's simple! It can be crossed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.90,0:06:50.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,簡単さ　渡れるに決まってる
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.61,0:06:55.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや　渡るぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.61,0:06:55.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１人残らず 全員渡る！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.62,0:06:53.34,default,,0,0,0,,No...! We can easily cross it!\NNo one will be left behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.64,0:06:54.85,default,,0,0,0,,Everyone will cross!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.51,0:06:57.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,渡る…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.51,0:06:59.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,渡る
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.67,0:06:56.45,default,,0,0,0,,We'll cross it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.74,0:06:57.45,default,,0,0,0,,We'll cross it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.85,0:06:59.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,渡る！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.97,0:07:01.57,default,,0,0,0,,- We'll cross it!\N- We'll cross it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.78,0:07:01.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,渡る
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.78,0:07:01.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,渡る！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.57,0:07:05.33,default,,0,0,0,,- We'll cross it! Let's go!\N- Yeah, let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.72,0:07:05.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,渡ろう　行ける
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.72,0:07:05.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだ　行けるぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.25,0:07:08.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,チャチャッと渡って
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.25,0:07:08.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんな所から おさらばしようぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.33,0:07:08.97,default,,0,0,0,,Let's hurry up, cross this and say\Nfarewell to a place like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.97,0:07:11.75,default,,0,0,0,,We'll be free from\Nthe burden of the debts,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.99,0:07:12.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちを押さえつけてきた
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.99,0:07:12.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカな借金 忌まわしい重しを
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.75,0:07:14.40,default,,0,0,0,,those heavy deadweight\Nin our lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.86,0:07:16.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人生からどけるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.86,0:07:16.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.40,0:07:15.83,default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.07,0:07:19.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのために ここ１回を勝とう
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.12,0:07:19.64,default,,0,0,0,,For that to happen,\Nwe need to win this once!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.90,0:07:23.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝ちきる　俺たちはできる
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.97,0:07:21.94,default,,0,0,0,,We need to win this cleanly!\NWe can do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.37,0:07:27.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちは押してくる敵がいる橋を
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.37,0:07:27.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一度 やり遂げてるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.47,0:07:27.28,default,,0,0,0,,We're done with crossing the bridge\Nthat had enemies pushing us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.61,0:07:30.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それに比べたら
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.61,0:07:30.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はるかに簡単　楽勝だ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.74,0:07:30.93,default,,0,0,0,,Compared to that,\Nthis task is easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.98,0:07:32.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちはやれる
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.07,0:07:32.09,default,,0,0,0,,We can do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.09,0:07:33.28,default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.28,0:07:34.44,default,,0,0,0,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.15,0:07:37.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やれる
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.15,0:07:37.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.27,0:07:36.02,default,,0,0,0,,It can be done!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.25,0:07:37.75,default,,0,0,0,,- That's right!\N- Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.09,0:07:40.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.09,0:07:40.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やれるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.18,0:07:39.36,default,,0,0,0,,It can be done!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.84,0:07:43.36,default,,0,0,0,,- Yeah! It can be done!\N- We can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.39,0:07:45.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やれる
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.39,0:07:45.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やれるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.23,0:07:48.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まるで悲鳴だな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.35,0:07:47.10,default,,0,0,0,,To me, it's a cry\Nof desperation!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.20,0:07:50.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あおられて その気になる
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.42,0:07:52.77,default,,0,0,0,,They are getting fired up\Nover that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.50,0:07:55.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなものは偽りの奮起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.50,0:07:55.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,エセもいいとこ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.00,0:07:56.61,default,,0,0,0,,That is a false encouragement...\NAll lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.10,0:08:00.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,目を背けているだけだ　真実から
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.40,0:07:58.82,default,,0,0,0,,Make believe may be good,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.31,0:08:03.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,内心は恐怖に身も心も震えている
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.37,0:08:03.48,default,,0,0,0,,but it just blinds the person\Nfrom reality...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.81,0:08:06.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あんな まやかしの決起は
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.86,0:08:05.85,default,,0,0,0,,They are shivering\Nwith fear inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.12,0:08:09.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そう 橋に乗って
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.12,0:08:09.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,５メートルで吹っ飛ぶ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.17,0:08:09.51,default,,0,0,0,,As one walks 5 metres into the bridge,\Nthat false motivation will vanish.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.65,0:08:12.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして真実が顔を出す
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.79,0:08:11.85,default,,0,0,0,,And then reality will smack\Nthem right in the face!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.12,0:08:14.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やつらは恐ろしいのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.16,0:08:15.96,default,,0,0,0,,They are afraid.\NIt's because they are afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.06,0:08:18.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,恐ろしいからこそ ああして
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.06,0:08:18.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自分を奮い立たせ 酔っている
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.96,0:08:18.59,default,,0,0,0,,That's why they get\Nthemselves drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.89,0:08:22.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それはあの男 カイジも同様
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.00,0:08:22.10,default,,0,0,0,,That man, Kaiji...\Nwill face the same situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.57,0:08:25.69,default,,0,0,0,,Really? Well, at least, he...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.60,0:08:25.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうでしょうか？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.60,0:08:25.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,少なくとも やつは…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.50,0:08:30.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,連中をあおってる時 やつの言葉が
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.50,0:08:30.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,変化していったのに気づいたか？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.69,0:08:30.47,default,,0,0,0,,When firing those people up, didn't\Nyou notice changes in his words?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.94,0:08:33.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,変化？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.94,0:08:33.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最初 あの男は
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.96,0:08:31.67,default,,0,0,0,,Changes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.35,0:08:36.36,default,,0,0,0,,At first that man said,\N"We'll cross this bridge".
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.84,0:08:36.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,｢この橋を渡る｣と言っていたが
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.51,0:08:39.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,途中でそれは｢できる｣になり
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.57,0:08:41.55,default,,0,0,0,,Then it was "Can be done". And at\Nthe end, it became "Can do".
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.01,0:08:41.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,話の終わりでは｢やれる｣になった
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.82,0:08:44.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜだか分かるか？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.84,0:08:43.25,default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.45,0:08:47.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,恐れているんだ やつも
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.48,0:08:46.96,default,,0,0,0,,He's afraid as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.36,0:08:52.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,恐れているからこそ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.36,0:08:52.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,｢渡る｣という直接的な表現を避け
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.43,0:08:52.21,default,,0,0,0,,Because he's afraid,\Nhe didn't use terms like "cross",
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.19,0:08:55.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,｢できる｣｢やれる｣などと
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.19,0:08:55.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,言いかえた
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.21,0:08:54.70,default,,0,0,0,,and changed it to "can be done"\Nand "can do".
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.16,0:08:59.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,無意識に逃げているんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.16,0:08:59.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,｢渡る｣という行為からな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.44,0:08:59.70,default,,0,0,0,,He's subconsciously evading the\Nact of walking across the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.87,0:09:05.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,言葉とは裏腹に その内心は
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.87,0:09:05.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,恐怖に震えているわけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.98,0:09:04.44,default,,0,0,0,,Despite what he said,\Nhe's really afraid too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.21,0:09:11.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,恐ろしい　恐ろしい
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.21,0:09:11.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,恐ろしい　恐ろしい
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.28,0:09:09.14,default,,0,0,0,,Afraid... Afraid... Afraid...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.07,0:09:11.68,default,,0,0,0,,Afraid...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.75,0:09:13.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,恐ろしい…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.86,0:09:13.19,default,,0,0,0,,Afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.56,0:09:22.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,盛り上がってるところ すまないが
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.72,0:09:24.42,default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, but the cutoff time\Nfor the exchange is 1:30am.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.06,0:09:25.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,換金の締め切りは午前１時半
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.46,0:09:31.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今 ０時25分　そろそろ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.46,0:09:31.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,出発したほうが賢明だと思うが？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.47,0:09:30.53,default,,0,0,0,,It's 12:25 am now.\NShouldn't we begin this soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.83,0:09:34.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,出発の時 来たる
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.86,0:09:34.48,default,,0,0,0,,The time to depart\Nhas come!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.77,0:09:37.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,恐れるな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.77,0:09:37.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,できるぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.90,0:09:39.55,default,,0,0,0,,- Don't be scared! It can be done!\N- It can be done! Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.34,0:09:39.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,できる
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.34,0:09:39.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,負けるな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.55,0:09:41.41,default,,0,0,0,,- Nakamura!\N- It can be done!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.64,0:09:41.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,中村　できる！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.58,0:09:44.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は さっきの橋では
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.58,0:09:44.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ぶっちぎりの１位
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.69,0:09:46.14,default,,0,0,0,,I arrived first on the previous\Nbridge! No one even came close!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.85,0:09:48.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,影も踏ませなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.85,0:09:48.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それと同じことをやるだけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.53,0:09:48.04,default,,0,0,0,,I just have to repeat my feat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.04,0:09:49.08,default,,0,0,0,,That's right, Nakamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.05,0:09:49.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだ 中村！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.05,0:09:49.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,同じことだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.08,0:09:49.98,default,,0,0,0,,It's the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.99,0:09:53.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,できる　できる　できる
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.15,0:09:53.72,default,,0,0,0,,It can be done!\NIt can be done!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.72,0:09:56.92,default,,0,0,0,,This is definitely possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.79,0:09:56.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これは できることなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.01,0:10:15.10,default,,0,0,0,,He's off!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.01,0:10:17.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,行った…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.01,0:10:17.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,行け！中村
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.47,0:10:19.98,default,,0,0,0,,- Go, Nakamura! You can do it!\N- Go, go, go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.45,0:10:21.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,中村　行け！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.45,0:10:21.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,行け！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.24,0:10:22.90,default,,0,0,0,,- Well done, keep it up!\N- Na-Nakamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.12,0:10:23.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,な 中村…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.12,0:10:23.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,行け　行けるぞ 太田
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.90,0:10:24.98,default,,0,0,0,,- You can do it! Oota!\N- Go, go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.39,0:10:28.45,default,,0,0,0,,- Go! Continue!\N- Keep that up, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.42,0:10:31.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,太田　いいぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.42,0:10:31.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,行け 太田！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.45,0:10:31.46,default,,0,0,0,,Oota, go for it!\NWell done, Oota!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.46,0:10:34.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,中村が口火を切ると
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.46,0:10:34.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それに引っ張られるように
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.72,0:10:36.19,default,,0,0,0,,With Nakamura off, they\Ncontinued along one by one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.90,0:10:38.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,次々と続いた
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.19,0:10:38.19,default,,0,0,0,,Sahara, carry on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.63,0:10:40.80,default,,0,0,0,,That is the reason for\N their morale.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.63,0:10:41.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのさまは戦意の発露
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.50,0:10:45.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,強気に意を決して
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.50,0:10:45.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自分の人生を切り開こうとする
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.54,0:10:45.57,default,,0,0,0,,Their firm belief is cutting off what\Nhas burdened them in their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.47,0:10:48.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな行為に見える
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.57,0:10:47.04,default,,0,0,0,,That is how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.38,0:10:51.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,続け！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.38,0:10:51.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おおっ　西田！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.53,0:10:49.77,default,,0,0,0,,I can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.99,0:10:51.77,default,,0,0,0,,That's right, you can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.15,0:10:54.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,続け！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.15,0:10:54.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.45,0:10:55.78,default,,0,0,0,,- Kaiji! Kaiji!\N- However, it is not the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.12,0:10:56.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,が 違う
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.12,0:10:59.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,違う　これは決意なんかじゃねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.29,0:10:59.52,default,,0,0,0,,This isn't determination.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.86,0:11:01.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いっときの激情に酔い
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.98,0:11:04.29,default,,0,0,0,,This is just a moment of frenzy.\NIt's trying to suppress true feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.86,0:11:04.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まっとうな感覚を
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.86,0:11:04.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,吹っ飛ばそうとする
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.99,0:11:08.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,単なる勢い　勢いだけ…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.02,0:11:07.76,default,,0,0,0,,This is just pure will,\Npure will...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.56,0:11:11.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ごまかし… だが
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.61,0:11:10.02,default,,0,0,0,,I'm merely deceiving myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.36,0:11:14.64,default,,0,0,0,,But for now... I have to...\NI have to... believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.47,0:11:14.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今は… 今は酔わなきゃダメ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.92,0:11:23.37,default,,0,0,0,,That's because this is\Nan escape route!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.94,0:11:23.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜなら これは離脱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.87,0:11:23.37,kaiji-main-top,,0,0,0,,Kaiji, Kaiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.95,0:11:28.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,己が存在の基盤
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.95,0:11:28.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大地からの離脱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.14,0:11:27.74,default,,0,0,0,,An escape from the root of our\Nexistence! An escape from reality!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.11,0:11:30.35,default,,0,0,0,,One who is completely sane\Nwould never do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.15,0:11:30.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まっとうな神経じゃ踏み出せねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.45,0:11:32.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,時 ０時40分
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.51,0:11:32.78,default,,0,0,0,,It's 12:40 am now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.92,0:11:36.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,希望のゴールへと続く
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.92,0:11:36.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ファイナルレース
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.04,0:11:36.24,default,,0,0,0,,The final hurdle to achieve\Nthe goal of hope continues...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.49,0:11:39.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死の橋渡り 開始
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.53,0:11:39.12,default,,0,0,0,,The crossing of\Nthe death bridge begins!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.99,0:11:54.54,default,,0,0,0,,Everyone was silent on the bridge.\NThe shouts at the start were gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.00,0:11:51.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,スタートまでの騒ぎとは
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.00,0:11:51.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,打って変わり
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.90,0:11:54.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,橋に踏み出してからは皆 無言
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.51,0:11:56.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,せき払い１つない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.54,0:11:56.35,default,,0,0,0,,Nobody even dared to cough.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.74,0:12:01.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,圧倒的な闇と静寂の中を
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.74,0:12:01.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただ10人は行く
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.81,0:12:01.58,default,,0,0,0,,The ten of them just carried on,\Nengulfed by the darkness and silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.46,0:12:07.24,default,,0,0,0,,Don't think about it!\NLet it go from the head!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.48,0:12:07.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,考えるな　マヒさせろ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.45,0:12:12.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自分の中にある感覚を遮断
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.45,0:12:12.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,眠らせろ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.60,0:12:12.09,default,,0,0,0,,Let the feeling within myself\Nbe gone... Let it go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.76,0:12:17.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,集中するんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.76,0:12:17.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,前に進むことだけに
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.80,0:12:16.49,default,,0,0,0,,Concentrate!\NJust move forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.33,0:12:20.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジは懸命に
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.33,0:12:20.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,抑えようとしていた
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.39,0:12:20.53,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji tries to push away \Nthe anxieties within him,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.93,0:12:24.83,default,,0,0,0,,and the devilish voice\Ninside his heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.97,0:12:25.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,心の中にある深い闇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.97,0:12:25.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,魔物の声を
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.64,0:12:28.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そしてそれは ほかの者も同じ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.64,0:12:28.46,default,,0,0,0,,And that is the same\Nfor the rest of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.44,0:12:31.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,皆 懸命に抑えつけていた
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.46,0:12:31.30,default,,0,0,0,,Everyone is desperately\Nforcing it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.31,0:12:37.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もうメッキは剥がれた
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.31,0:12:37.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さっきまでの大騒ぎは
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.47,0:12:35.27,default,,0,0,0,,The coating has already\Ncome undone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.69,0:12:40.58,default,,0,0,0,,The wild noises made earlier\Nresembled cheap rocket fireworks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.62,0:12:41.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,言うなら
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.62,0:12:41.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,安物のロケット花火のようなもの
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.02,0:12:47.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,橋に乗った途端
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.02,0:12:47.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,心は冷え 恐怖が頭をもたげる
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.09,0:12:45.50,default,,0,0,0,,The instant they got on the bridge,\Ntheir hearts froze and fear emerged.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.13,0:12:52.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もうすぐ開く
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.13,0:12:52.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,魔物を招き入れての宴の扉がな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.25,0:12:48.64,default,,0,0,0,,It will soon open...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.93,0:12:52.66,default,,0,0,0,,The door into the feast which \Nthey were invited to by demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.43,0:12:59.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人は生まれながら
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.43,0:12:59.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,心の中に魔物を飼っている
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.46,0:12:59.18,default,,0,0,0,,As humans grow, they\Nfeed the demon within as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.71,0:13:02.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,普段は心の最も深い部屋に
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.71,0:13:02.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,閉じ込め
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.83,0:13:02.98,default,,0,0,0,,Normally, that devil's locked \Nwithin the depths of the darkness,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.71,0:13:06.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,鍵をかけ 忘れようとしている
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.98,0:13:05.70,default,,0,0,0,,and is locked away,\Nforgotten...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.48,0:13:08.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.62,0:13:07.61,default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.02,0:13:13.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,鍵も扉も所詮 無力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.04,0:13:13.46,default,,0,0,0,,In the end, the door and\Nthe lock are totally useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.46,0:13:17.58,default,,0,0,0,,In just moments, that demon\Nwill break loose and appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.49,0:13:17.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなもの あっという間に
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.49,0:13:17.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こじあけて 現れる怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.26,0:13:23.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死という名の魔物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.34,0:13:22.33,default,,0,0,0,,"Death" is the name\Nof that demon...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.03,0:13:26.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それがまもなく連中を襲う
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.14,0:13:25.79,default,,0,0,0,,And that will strike them\Nvery soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.67,0:13:30.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人の夢や希望　目標
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.71,0:13:28.60,default,,0,0,0,,The hopes and dreams\Nof humans...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.03,0:13:33.40,default,,0,0,0,,Their targets, plans,\Ncooperation and sincerity,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.24,0:13:33.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,計画　協力や親切
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.61,0:13:36.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,愛情　優しさ…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.80,0:13:35.92,default,,0,0,0,,love and kindness...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.51,0:13:41.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのすべてを握りつぶす
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.51,0:13:41.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,魔物の中の魔物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.62,0:13:40.98,default,,0,0,0,,All that will be crushed,\Nby the demon amongst the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.35,0:13:46.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,生きとし 生ける者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.35,0:13:46.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すべてを支配している死の恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.48,0:13:46.00,default,,0,0,0,,All living creatures are \Ncontrolled by the fear of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.12,0:13:50.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その圧倒的かつ冷酷な真実
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.31,0:13:49.58,default,,0,0,0,,That is the overwhelming\Ncold, hard truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.32,0:13:54.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それをやつらは
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.32,0:13:54.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの橋の上で思い出す
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.52,0:13:54.07,default,,0,0,0,,Those guys on the bridge\Nwill think of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.65,0:14:16.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これほど違うものか
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.80,0:14:15.76,default,,0,0,0,,It's not that different!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.02,0:14:19.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,落ちても助かるという状況と
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.02,0:14:19.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,落ちたら死ぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.06,0:14:19.98,default,,0,0,0,,To fall and still be safe,\Nand to fall and die.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.89,0:14:22.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,即死という状況では これほど…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.98,0:14:23.11,default,,0,0,0,,The situation known as \Ncertain death is not so different!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.57,0:14:37.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やば… 嫌な気分だぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.75,0:14:36.53,default,,0,0,0,,This is bad... \NI have a bad feeling about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.37,0:14:41.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何かが胸の中に湧いてきてる
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.53,0:14:40.44,default,,0,0,0,,Something is swelling up\Nwithin my heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.64,0:14:44.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まるで心臓を
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.77,0:14:47.95,default,,0,0,0,,It's as if cold hands are\Ngripping my heart tightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.44,0:14:48.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,冷えた両手で
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.44,0:14:48.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしづかみにされるような
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.25,0:14:50.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな悪寒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.33,0:14:49.71,default,,0,0,0,,That devilish coldness...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.54,0:14:56.78,default,,0,0,0,,Bad... This is bad...!\NThis feeling is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.55,0:14:55.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まずい… まずい！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.35,0:14:59.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この感情は
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.09,0:15:02.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この感情は 俺を殺す
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.20,0:15:02.97,default,,0,0,0,,This feeling...\Nwill get me killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.90,0:15:09.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,殺される　クソッ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.92,0:15:06.29,default,,0,0,0,,I'm being killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.91,0:15:11.87,default,,0,0,0,,Darn it! What should I do?!\NWhat should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.17,0:15:12.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうしたらいい？どうしたら…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.88,0:15:21.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何だよ　何だよ これ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.03,0:15:20.03,default,,0,0,0,,What's this? What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.81,0:15:24.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しっかりしろ しっかり
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.94,0:15:24.27,default,,0,0,0,,Get a grip! Get a...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.34,0:15:45.53,default,,0,0,0,,W-What was it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.34,0:15:47.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,な 何だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.54,0:15:50.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何なんだよ 今の
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.56,0:15:49.23,default,,0,0,0,,W-What was that...\Njust now...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.44,0:15:52.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,変だぞ 俺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.64,0:15:52.09,default,,0,0,0,,This is strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.44,0:15:57.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺の体が 俺のものじゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.44,0:15:57.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ないみたいな この感覚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.59,0:15:56.12,default,,0,0,0,,This feeling is as if \Nmy body is no longer mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.58,0:16:01.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フワフワして…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.58,0:16:01.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんな調子じゃ とても無理
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.61,0:16:01.17,default,,0,0,0,,I feel unsteady. With this\Ncondition, it is impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.45,0:16:05.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,渡れない　落ちちまう
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.45,0:16:05.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,落ち…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.52,0:16:03.28,default,,0,0,0,,I can't cross...\NI'll fall...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.54,0:16:05.28,default,,0,0,0,,I'll fall...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.76,0:16:15.41,default,,0,0,0,,I don't like this...!\NI don't want to fall...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.77,0:16:16.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,嫌だ　落ちたくない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.10,0:16:20.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,落ちたくない　落ちたくない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.17,0:16:19.20,default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to fall!\N I don't want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.44,0:16:23.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,生きたい　生きたい
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.50,0:16:23.11,default,,0,0,0,,I want to live!\NI want to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.34,0:16:25.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,生きたい！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.40,0:16:24.80,default,,0,0,0,,I want to live!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.74,0:16:28.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,金もいらない　何もいらない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.79,0:16:28.64,default,,0,0,0,,I don't need money,\NI don't need anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.68,0:16:33.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,40まで借金生活でもいい
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.68,0:16:33.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何でもいいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.93,0:16:32.34,default,,0,0,0,,It's okay to be in debt till\NI'm 40! Anything is fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.19,0:16:36.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただ生きたい
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.20,0:16:34.72,default,,0,0,0,,I just want to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.09,0:16:40.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんな…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.09,0:16:40.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんな簡単で単純なことに
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.29,0:16:40.32,default,,0,0,0,,It was... \NIt was always so simple...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.69,0:16:45.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここまで…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.69,0:16:45.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここまで追い詰められなきゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.70,0:16:41.81,default,,0,0,0,,But up till now...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.31,0:16:44.18,default,,0,0,0,,It has always\Ndriven me all this while...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.32,0:16:46.65,default,,0,0,0,,To think that I didn't\Nrealise it until now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.40,0:16:47.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,気がつかないなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.77,0:16:59.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君　違うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.83,0:16:58.33,default,,0,0,0,,Kaiji... It's completely\Ndifferent!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.00,0:17:03.43,default,,0,0,0,,The previous bridge and\Nthis one are totally different!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.01,0:17:03.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さ さっきまでの橋と全然 違うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.82,0:17:06.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,言うな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.82,0:17:06.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,カイジ君
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.88,0:17:04.80,default,,0,0,0,,Don't say it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.02,0:17:07.00,default,,0,0,0,,- Kaiji...\N- Don't say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.29,0:17:08.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,言うな　同じだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.37,0:17:10.07,default,,0,0,0,,It's the same!\NIt is the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.75,0:17:12.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,同じなんだよ　何も変わらない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.04,0:17:12.44,default,,0,0,0,,Nothing has changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.92,0:17:14.42,default,,0,0,0,,Nothing has changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.93,0:17:16.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,変わらないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.90,0:17:20.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,風…？風だ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.01,0:17:18.03,default,,0,0,0,,The wind!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.76,0:17:20.55,default,,0,0,0,,There's wind!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.70,0:17:23.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,冗談じゃねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.62,0:17:24.55,default,,0,0,0,,You're kidding me! If the wind\Nstarts to blow now...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.04,0:17:25.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今 風なんかにあおられたら…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.58,0:17:40.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,吹いてない　吹いてないぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.70,0:17:39.57,default,,0,0,0,,It's not blowing,\NIt is not blowing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.12,0:17:42.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本当だ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.19,0:17:42.07,default,,0,0,0,,It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.49,0:17:46.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,吹いてない　気のせいだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.59,0:17:45.08,default,,0,0,0,,No, it's just your imagination!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.29,0:17:50.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何言ってんだよ　風だよ　風が！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.34,0:17:49.58,default,,0,0,0,,What nonsense are you saying?!\NThere is wind!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.54,0:17:52.58,default,,0,0,0,,Oota?! Oota, \Nhang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.56,0:17:52.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,太田！太田　しっかりしろ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.80,0:17:55.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,飛ばされるー
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.93,0:17:55.58,default,,0,0,0,,I'm being blown away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.73,0:17:59.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,太田　顔を上げろ　上げろったら
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.93,0:17:59.09,default,,0,0,0,,Oota!! Look up! I said look up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.30,0:18:03.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よく見るんだ　吹いてない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.30,0:18:03.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,風は吹いてない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.36,0:18:02.59,default,,0,0,0,,Look carefully! It's not blowing!\NThe wind isn't blowing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.18,0:18:05.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,落ち着け 太田　落ち着け
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.38,0:18:05.59,default,,0,0,0,,Calm down, Oota!\NCalm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.88,0:18:10.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,太田！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.92,0:18:10.55,default,,0,0,0,,Oota...!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.59,0:18:16.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,始まったな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.63,0:18:15.14,default,,0,0,0,,It has begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.49,0:18:18.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,風…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.49,0:18:18.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,太田
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.52,0:18:19.52,default,,0,0,0,,- The wind. Wind!\N- Oota, Oota!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.46,0:18:22.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,太田　お前が
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.46,0:18:22.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,風だと感じているのは幻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.52,0:18:23.96,default,,0,0,0,,The wind you're feeling is\Nan illusion! It's imaginary!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.90,0:18:27.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,幻覚だ　幻覚なんだ 太田
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.12,0:18:26.79,default,,0,0,0,,- Someone... Save me!\N- It's an illusion, Oota!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.17,0:18:30.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,助けて！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.17,0:18:30.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,落ち着け 太田
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.20,0:18:28.12,default,,0,0,0,,Save me!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.46,0:18:29.62,default,,0,0,0,,Calm down! Oota!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.40,0:18:35.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,と… 飛ばされる
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.40,0:18:35.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誰か！飛ばされる
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.32,0:18:34.83,default,,0,0,0,,I'm being blown away!\NCan someone... help me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.61,0:18:38.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ば… バカ野郎　触るな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.62,0:18:38.13,default,,0,0,0,,F-Fool! Don't touch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.51,0:18:42.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さっき見ただろ　その橋には
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.51,0:18:42.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,高圧電流が流れてんだぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.68,0:18:42.63,default,,0,0,0,,You saw it earlier, right? The bridge\Nhas high volts passing through!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.63,0:18:46.13,default,,0,0,0,,Sahara! What are you doing?!\NStop him! Support him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.68,0:18:46.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,佐原　何してる　止めろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.68,0:18:46.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,支えるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.32,0:18:48.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカ言うな　できるか そんなこと
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.36,0:18:48.64,default,,0,0,0,,Don't say such a stupid thing! \NI can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.59,0:18:50.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,佐原！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.59,0:18:50.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,無理だ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.64,0:18:50.86,default,,0,0,0,,- Sahara!\N- It's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.82,0:18:53.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここで人を支えるなんて無理！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.86,0:18:52.64,default,,0,0,0,,It's impossible\Nto support someone here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.36,0:18:56.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自分がバランスを取るので
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.36,0:18:56.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,精いっぱいなんだぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.40,0:18:56.24,default,,0,0,0,,I'm already at my wit's end \Ntrying to maintain my balance!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.16,0:18:58.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,巻き添え食ったら
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.16,0:18:58.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺まで感電して落ちちまうんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.24,0:18:59.65,default,,0,0,0,,If I get dragged into it, \NI'll lose it and fall too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.76,0:19:01.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,冗談じゃねえ　救えねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.03,0:19:04.94,default,,0,0,0,,I can't save him! I can't do\Na single thing about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.76,0:19:02.65,kaiji-main-top,,0,0,0,,I'm being blown away!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.27,0:19:04.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうにもならねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.27,0:19:04.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうにもならねえよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.90,0:19:08.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,太田　聞こえるか？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.90,0:19:08.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やめろ　触るな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.94,0:19:08.65,default,,0,0,0,,Oota! Can you hear me?!\NStop it! Don't touch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.65,0:19:11.39,default,,0,0,0,,- Don't touch it!\N- Look at me! Oota, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.87,0:19:11.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺を見ろ 太田　見ろ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.28,0:19:13.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見るんだ 太田　見ろ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.39,0:19:14.73,default,,0,0,0,,Look, Oota, look at me!\NLook here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.70,0:19:13.56,kaiji-main-top,,0,0,0,,No, please!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.51,0:19:17.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こっちを見ろ　見ろったら
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.51,0:19:17.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,頼むから見てくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.73,0:19:17.78,default,,0,0,0,,Look at me!\NPlease look at me, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.18,0:19:20.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見ろ　俺を見ろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.18,0:19:20.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誰か助けて！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.78,0:19:20.40,default,,0,0,0,,- Look at me!\N- Someone save me!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.69,0:19:23.90,default,,0,0,0,,Look, Oota! Oota!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.72,0:19:23.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見るんだ 太田　太田！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.69,0:19:27.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,太田！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.90,0:19:26.91,default,,0,0,0,,Oota!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.42,0:19:55.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１人…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.43,0:19:54.93,default,,0,0,0,,One person.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.60,0:20:06.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,太田…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.63,0:20:05.94,default,,0,0,0,,Oota...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.07,0:20:13.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう 嫌だ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.13,0:20:12.15,default,,0,0,0,,I don't... want this anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.54,0:20:15.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう嫌だ　こんな橋！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.65,0:20:15.90,default,,0,0,0,,I had enough of this bridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.84,0:20:18.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,落ち着け 秋川　落ち着け
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.90,0:20:18.19,default,,0,0,0,,Calm down, Akikawa! Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.08,0:20:20.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,嫌だ　戻る　戻ろう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.19,0:20:20.58,default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm heading back!\NLet's go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.55,0:20:22.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よせ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.58,0:20:21.93,default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.72,0:20:39.13,default,,0,0,0,,Go back please!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.93,0:20:41.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誰か…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.93,0:20:41.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,石田さん
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.13,0:20:41.33,default,,0,0,0,,- Ishida!! \N- Someone... Someone help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.00,0:20:43.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,落ち着け　みんな落ち着け
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.33,0:20:43.61,default,,0,0,0,,Calm down!\NEveryone calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.77,0:20:47.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誰か！死にたくない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.79,0:20:47.62,default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.67,0:20:49.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,落ち着け
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.86,0:20:49.18,default,,0,0,0,,Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.19,0:20:55.19,default,,0,0,0,,Save me... Save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.45,0:20:55.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,助けて… 助けてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.03,0:21:00.70,default,,0,0,0,,Calm down, everyone!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.15,0:21:02.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,落ち着くんだ　みんな！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.55,0:21:05.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,時 ０時44分
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.56,0:21:05.18,default,,0,0,0,,It's 12:44 am now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.39,0:21:08.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,命をかけた ファイナルレース
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.49,0:21:09.70,default,,0,0,0,,There're 8 persons left betting\Ntheir lives on the final race.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.03,0:21:10.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,残り８名
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.40,0:21:15.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その先に待つのは希望の光か
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.40,0:21:15.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それとも
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.41,0:21:14.08,default,,0,0,0,,Does the light of hope\Nawait in front of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.08,0:21:18.04,default,,0,0,0,,Or is it the darkness of \Nhopelessness?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.23,0:21:17.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,絶望という名の闇か
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.29,0:22:45.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,次回 ｢亡霊｣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.35,0:22:45.53,default,,0,0,0,,Next, Dying Spirit.
